## Telegram Bots

- For Telegram bots, use **aiogram** library (version 3.0.0+)
- Recommended structure:
  - `app/main.py` - bot entry point
  - `handlers/` - ONLY Telegram message and callback handlers (commands, text messages, callbacks)
  - `services/` - business logic (auth_service, manager_service, employer_service, etc.)
  - `utils/` - utilities for messages and helper functions (message_utils.py for message formatting/validation)
  - `keyboards/` - bot keyboards (reply and inline keyboards)
  - `repositories/` - DB work
  - `models/` - data models

